e="implied">Frau</rs> von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10818" subtype="implied">uns Beiden</rs> alles Schön<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te und Be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te!</p><closer>Dein alter<lb/><signed>Hermann</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><tei:person xml:id="pmb10815">
